text: Brachynarthron unicoloripennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1968. It is known from the Ivory Coast.BioLib.cz - Brachynarthron unicoloripennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1968
